name: FEditorScriptingMeshReductionSettings_Deprecated
doc: Deprecated as of 5.0, use the struct FStaticMeshReductionSettings in Static Mesh Editor Library Instead

PercentTriangles: Percentage of triangles to keep. Ranges from 0.0 to 1.0: 1.0 = no reduction, 0.0 = no triangles.
ScreenSize: ScreenSize to display this LOD. Ranges from 0.0 to 1.0.
